{"tid":557740,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"日本緊急食糧試食報告","createTime":"2018-02-11T15:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T12:31:42.000Z","uid":126221,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6eaed36138753452218e7cea223c9354b8dda2","tid":557740,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"因為之前既工作關係，經常會留意一 d 可以儲存好耐既食物，<br />\n例如 MRE，罐頭，granola bar ... 等。<br />\n今次試食既，係早排由日本買既緊急食糧 - 松茸飯。<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，放相先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/232143_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F232143_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg&h=b0c999c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/232146_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F232146_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg&h=59e63727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打開包裝，內有膠匙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/232149_f99687dd719c4e8bc6a39e946c3d9ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F232149_f99687dd719c4e8bc6a39e946c3d9ef7.jpg&h=cf7c8f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n注水後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/232152_2de40e0d504f583cda7465979f958a98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F232152_2de40e0d504f583cda7465979f958a98.jpg&h=2900abb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n看看有什麼成份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/232154_135007e7085979a7d5b41ce54c0e54d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F232154_135007e7085979a7d5b41ce54c0e54d7.jpg&h=a81ed5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/232156_fac4ef5554f69012fe38d2f1d4e245a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F232156_fac4ef5554f69012fe38d2f1d4e245a6.jpg&h=ea19b502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成品 close up<br />\n<br />\n今次食既係尾西出品既松茸飯。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.onisifoods.co.jp/products/matsutake.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onisifoods.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fmatsutake.html&d=cTbfhFij%2FhRN8MJ5IHlsRcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1f977e3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.onisifoods.co.jp/products/matsutake.html</a><br />\n日本都幾興呢類形乾燥飯。<br />\n只需要加熱水等十五分鐘 (又或者常溫水等一個鐘)，就可以食到一個尚算正常既飯。<br />\n<br />\n口感方面，比較軟身，作為長期儲糧黎講都唔錯。<br />\n氣味方面，未煮時就有 d 菇味 (霉味)，煮好就消失左。<br />\n味道呢，比較淡口，食唔出 d 菇味。反而 d 醬油腐皮絲滲出黎既味令到個飯更好食。<br />\n<br />\n總括黎講，作為儲糧尚算不錯，體積細，重量輕，可長期存放 (約 5 年)。<br />\n但如果對飯質有要求就唔好考慮了。份量亦只能夠話女仔份量，飯桶不宜。<br />\n<br />\n下次再去日本時再買多幾款口味，或者其他緊急食糧，到時再出報告。<br />\n<br />\n完畢。"},{"pid":"49487771867eda5034596cf0a8b7cbd5e863d7bc","tid":557740,"uid":3131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"兩包應唔應付到體力勞動時候既一餐?"},{"pid":"84201b38a00d01be4cc3bce34947a554a181ff79","tid":557740,"uid":126221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49487771867eda5034596cf0a8b7cbd5e863d7bc","tid":557740,"uid":3131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"兩包應唔應付到體力勞動時候既一餐?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"應該唔夠。<br />\n<br />\n你預一包等於一碗飯左右。<br />\n正常體力勞動既人應該要起碼兩袋一餐，<br />\n唔係話佢熱量唔夠，而係根本唔夠飽既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n帶去外國止飯癮，又或者用黎當下午茶就 OK 既。"},{"pid":"467ef0cc4c2814b53507e49706918166f82d7fff","tid":557740,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"咁都要出報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf591f730d1317a156afc6de349868fa2f40535","tid":557740,"uid":25028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"好似幾得意"},{"pid":"8a1cd489eb439c543924d9f556bada15ca79135d","tid":557740,"uid":11506,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"467ef0cc4c2814b53507e49706918166f82d7fff","tid":557740,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"咁都要出報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"你叫一次春都開一次post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a5825616ed9ea059f52e5ba92dd5b8bed20cac","tid":557740,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8a1cd489eb439c543924d9f556bada15ca79135d","tid":557740,"uid":11506,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"467ef0cc4c2814b53507e49706918166f82d7fff","tid":557740,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"咁都要出報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"你叫一次春都開一次post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"呢d同鑵頭即食麵差唔多<br />\n入到黎有d失望"},{"pid":"0d1c7c9a287769e786a90eee320bec55ffad6ea2","tid":557740,"uid":126221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"49487771867eda5034596cf0a8b7cbd5e863d7bc","tid":557740,"uid":3131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"兩包應唔應付到體力勞動時候既一餐?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，頭先眼殘睇錯左。<br />\n<br />\n一包份量唔夠，熱量勉強。<br />\n兩包份量 OK，熱量足夠。<br />\n三包 ... 無謂啦，頂住檔放工去食餐好既好過啦。"},{"pid":"d37e399c89700b7dff3961dded037cd0448ac74a","tid":557740,"uid":9736,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"467ef0cc4c2814b53507e49706918166f82d7fff","tid":557740,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":24,"sc